							<p>NME is a complete cross platform game engine which leverage Haxe to be one of the best
								tool to build
								mobile and web games. Based on the familiar Flash API, NME runs native on every device.
							</p>
							<a href="http://nme.io">nme.io</a>
						</div>
					</div>

					<hr/>
					
					<div class="row">

						<div class="fifth">
							<img src="img/foundation/neko.jpg" alt="neko"/>
						</div>

						<div class="fourfifth">
							<h3>Neko</h3>							
							<p>Neko is a high-level dynamicly typed programming language. It can be used as an embedded scripting language. 
							It has been designed to provide a common runtime for several different languages.</p>
							<a href="http://nekovm.org/">nekovm.org</a>

						</div>
					</div>
					
					<hr/>
					
				</div>

			</div>

		</div>

